<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=yes">
    <title>Mise à jour sécurité – RSSI</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            background: #f0f2f5;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, system-ui, sans-serif;
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .card {
            max-width: 580px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 32px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 35px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background: #1e3a5f;
            padding: 24px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .header p {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            margin-top: 6px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 28px 24px;
        }
        .alert {
            background: #fff3e0;
            border-left: 5px solid #e67e22;
            padding: 14px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            border-radius: 12px;
        }
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        label {
            display: block;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            color: #1e2a3a;
        }
        input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px 16px;
            border: 1.5px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 16px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: 0.2s;
            background: #fff;
        }
        input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #1e3a5f;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(30,58,95,0.2);
        }
        .btn-submit {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            background: #1e3a5f;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 14px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            border-radius: 40px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.2s;
            margin-top: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .btn-submit:hover {
            background: #0f2b44;
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }
        .footer-note {
            margin-top: 24px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: #64748b;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 520px) {
            body { padding: 10px; }
            .card { margin: 20px auto; }
            .content { padding: 20px; }
            input { padding: 12px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="card">
    <div class="header">
        <h1>🔐Sécurité des systèmes</h1>
        <p>Service RSSI – Mise à jour obligatoire</p>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="alert">
             Un renouvellement général des mots de passe est requis.  
            Veuillez saisir vos identifiants actuels pour générer vos nouveaux accès sécurisés.
        </div>
        <form method="post" action="{{ path('phishing_fake_submit') }}">
            <input type="hidden" name="token" value="{{ token }}">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>Mot de passe actuel de votre  PC</label>
                <input type="password" name="password_pc" autocomplete="off">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>Mot de passe actuel de votre wifi</label>
                <input type="password" name="password_wifi" autocomplete="off">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>Confirmer votre email professionnel</label>
                <input type="email" name="email" autocomplete="off">
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">Valider et recevoir nouveaux accès</button>
        </form>
        <div class="footer-note">
            Cette opération est confidentielle.<br>
            En cas de doute, contactez votre RSSI directement.
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>